text.tspan: Hope of Glory — Preparing for Christ’s Return
Just as the days of Noah were,
Coming of the Son of Man be.
The Lord will come to deal with man;
He will solve all our problems.
We much watch for our Lord—
Lord, I repent. Show me mercy.
Save me from the present age.
Lord, give me a glorious ending;
The Lord has a reward for us.
He has called us all upward,
To His Christ, for our prize
